Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeTom ShortPants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彬彬有礼  举止得体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's very well-mannered and always behaves
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeTom ShortPants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果打发时间是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If passing the time is something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeTom ShortPants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就去熟食店吃个薯泥饼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then go to a deli and eat a knish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeTom ShortPants
