Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去上班了  小蛞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I'm off to work, Barry
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我预备好了
