Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,280)}脆卷王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我预备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeTom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  靠谱的客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, reliable customers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  鱿鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Octward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就爱那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, SpongeTom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考虑到你明天就要放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On account of it being your day off tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就提前让你下班回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd let you go home early
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  爪老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Claws
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家宠物小蛞一定会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pet Barry sure is going to appreciate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟今晚可以早早开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,getting his dinner early tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了  因为讲得可对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amusing because it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你想象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagine, if you will
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.42,0:02:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作了一整天  照常坐公交下班回家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,taking your usual bus ride home after a long day's work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.05,0:02:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却累到睡着  坐过了站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you are so tired
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you fall asleep and miss your stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,径直坐到了潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and head straight for The Tidal Zone
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我在这里可以缩得很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I can be tiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,598)}潮间带
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,1028)}小蛞周一上午六点\N吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1362,1028)}小蛞周一下午五点\N吃的食物
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我出门期间这些应该够你吃了  小蛞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That should tide you over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I get back from my trip, Barry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不常有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that is peculiar
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门外没人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  把壳戴好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, put your shell on
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交到站了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bus has arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不在的时候要乖一点  小蛞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behave while I'm gone, Barry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚睡得可真是沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the deepest sleep I've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.36,0:03:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm late
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁给门把手挪了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who moved the doorknob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我镜子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to my mirror?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥皂片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soap flakes?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.18,0:04:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  上班迟到害得我这么心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, being late for work has really thrown me off my game
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeTom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(924,920)}宝  宝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上下动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们就动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, if you insist
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为你今天放假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was your day off
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是鱿鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Octward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.08,注释,,0,0,0,,[ awkward（尴尬的）与 Octward（鱿鱼哥）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was awkward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来蟹老板给厨房门挪了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess Mr. Krabs moved the kitchen door
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我烤架怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to my grill?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食材都被切碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ingredients have been shredded
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这面包好像被谁一屁股坐扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like these buns were under someone's buns
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一单了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An order
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该开工了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I better get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干嘛  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛围着厨师围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a cook's apron?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放假期间  我都代你班做玉米卷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I always cook the tacos on your day off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都没放过假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never taken a day off in my life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这单应该是玉米卷才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This order is supposed to be a taco
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人如果想吃美味堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the customer wanted a Yummy Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那早就去美之霸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they would have gone to The Yum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你怎么不是章鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, why aren't you an octopus?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有蟹老板  你怎么变蓝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, Mr. Krabs, why are you blue?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玉米卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tacos?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你个事  我名字叫鱿鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, for starters, my name is Octward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一只鱿鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm a squid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每周都给你放假是有原因的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I give you a day off every week for a reason, son
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还在上下动呢  汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still bobbing, Tom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉不觉得海绵汤姆今天有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did SpongeTom seem a little strange to you today?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他眼睛都长在胸口上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His eyes were on his chest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1092,920)}不 知 道 看 哪
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我都有点不自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't know where to look
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,698)}美之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会去海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At The Chum Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是视疲劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes must be tired
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1406,638)}眼镜店
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  这样看着好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, that looks better
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,模模糊糊的  很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blurry, but in a reassuring way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待会儿给派大星跟珊迪说说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait 'til I tell Patrick and Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今早遇到了什么怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what a strange morning I had
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There they are now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  能再见到你们俩可真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, am I glad to see you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意我吃你薯条吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind if I have some of your fries, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little dry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意我喝你汽水吗  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind if I have a sip of your soda, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太难喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天整天都乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This day has been bonkers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥变鱿鱼了  蟹老板又变蓝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward was a squid, Mr. Krabs was blue
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡又变玉米卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the Krabby Patties were tacos
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能撞见我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just so glad to run into my best pals
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星跟珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是派大星跟珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are Patrick and Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  我的名字可是派小星才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I assure you, good sir, my name is Preston
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不认识你说的那位派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know not of this Patrick you speak of
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话  我是珊米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duh, and me am Sammy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一只松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I be a squirrel folk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西一样还是乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything is still all crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202,346)}哈利健身房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(558,686)}停业
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈利健身房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harry's Gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124,260)}泡夫老师骑车学校
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡夫老师骑车学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Gruff's Biking School?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,520)}潮菲嬉皮伯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮菲嬉皮伯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Groovy Groupers?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴走小哥要路过你左边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Young Man Power Walker coming up on your left
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My arm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要去找爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must see my parents
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有爸妈  事情就能好转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Parents make everything okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  爸妈把家漆成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, my parents painted their house
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满怀希望的黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a nice hopeful yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是往眼睛里喷柠檬汁那套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ol' lemon juice in the eye trick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸妈的幽默感真是与日俱增
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My parents really have developed a sense of humor
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长得跟我不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look not quite exactly like me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这位怪模怪样的朋友是谁  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's your weird-looking friend, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他长得隐约有点眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He looks vaguely familiar
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐隐又约约
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very vague
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不是我爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not my parents
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把我爸妈怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do with my parents?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把大家都换成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've replaced everyone with
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,weirdos
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为自己能换掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think you can replace me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就只是一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all nothing but a bunch of
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,evil doppelgängers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群分身休想围攻我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't let you doppel-gang up on me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,728)}欢迎光临衣尾村
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临衣尾村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Welcome to Tankini Top"?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.68,0:09:47.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群臭分身毁了整个裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've ruined the whole town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you darn, dingy doppelgängers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor fella
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慌得晕了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got so overwhelmed, he fainted
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要拿他怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do with him?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议给他打包一份午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we give him a sack lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他送上离开这里的第一班公交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and put him on the first bus out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一趟公交之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674,278)}裤头村公交总站
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是在这发现他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where I found him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道他是怎么到这来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how he got here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was so worried
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就要代他做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd have to cook the Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要醒起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's starting to "un-asleepen"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再见到你们真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, am I glad to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚做了场特别怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had the strangest dream
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦见我醒来  裤头村的一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I woke up and everything in Bikini Bottom was
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变了样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,different
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你不在  而且你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you weren't there, and you weren't there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都懂  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get it, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're late
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我预备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,设想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Consider this:
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人都有一个分身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a doppelgänger
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how is one to know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁才是分  谁才是身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if they are the doppel or the gänger?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得到这问题的答案  就只能前去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A question that can only be answered in
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮间带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tidal Zone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.68,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp45\c&H00FFC1&}章鱼哥的\N{\fs30} \N{\fs175}强人假日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:10.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一年一度的假日总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, my annual day off
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.99,0:11:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是个精致无比的假日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A day filled with sophistication
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先吃顿讲究的早午餐  前去高档餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starting with a gourmet brunch at a fancy eatery
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汤匙俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sol de Soup Spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,446)}汤匙俱乐部\N克拉肯大道\N{\fnArial}617{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,克拉肯大道617号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,617 Kraken Avenue
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,617号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,617
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:41.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,176)}强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the place
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't be the place
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干嘛  高档弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want, fancy boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在汤匙俱乐部有预约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,made a reservation at Sol de Soup Spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这地址肯定不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but this couldn't possibly be the correct address
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it certainly is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我带你就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you to your table
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临汤匙俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sol de Soup Spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按照我们的念法就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or as we pronounce it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能先给你来杯饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I start you off with a beverage?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有什么推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any recommendations?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝尸寒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Cold Cadaver
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就有法国风情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds French
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Reg
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我们菜单上最强人的奶昔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's the toughest milkshake on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快  一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit, and bon voyage
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Très bien
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么还能活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you still alive?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.45,0:13:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, bub
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是俱乐部门卫雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Reg, the bouncer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.15,0:14:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't know who I am
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你还挺强人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be a pretty tough guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都喝了蓝尸寒还能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you drank the Cold Cadaver and lived
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着确实挺强人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that does sound pretty tough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你足够强人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may be tough enough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以荣登最强人之墙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to hang on the Wall of Toughest Guys
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886,398)}最强人之墙
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是鉴于你不记得自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But seein' as you don't remember your name
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能给你取个闻风丧胆的大名了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll have to give you a real intimidating one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gots it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.31,0:14:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a tough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure are, Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C'mon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出门去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's blow this joint
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一件要事  疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First things first, Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让你开鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we gotta get you on a hog
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  你可以先借我的开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, you can borrow mine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用这鬼火狠狠地炸街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's make this piggy squeal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Safety first
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我表现好吗  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I do good, Reg?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did great
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功伤害了十几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You managed to hurt at least a dozen people
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强人就得有双强脚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tough guys gotta have tough feet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在要干嘛  雷吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what now, Reg?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找几个小混混干架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We look for punks to pick fights with
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如那边那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that guy over there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:12.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,286)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.57,0:16:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个货真价实的停车标志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A genuine stop sign
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got this one, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个拍来拍去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Camera face
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如你来拍这个得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a picture of this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这味道臭得太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This smells amazingly bad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一击就把他给撂倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You took that guy out in one hit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这件皮衣是你应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've earned your leather
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,356)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方一看就适合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks like a good place
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闲混
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to loiter
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.27,0:17:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是要来到处闲混  欺负老百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We hang around and mess with the normies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind if I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃一半再蘸酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,double dip?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱闲混
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love loitering
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱死你新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love your new friends
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认识这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know this guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他当然认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course he does
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是邻居兼最好的朋友兼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're neighbors/best friends/
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同事兼最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coworkers/best friends
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都没见过这傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this chump in my life
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.56,0:18:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真在这垃圾堆工作  我妥妥一废物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'd be a real loser to work in a dump like this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一群小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loiter-er-ers?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟这群小混混一起混  章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you hanging around
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with these hooligans, Mister--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好有男子气概
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's so macho
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再这么男子气概下去就开除他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Macho" more of this and he's fired
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来这干嘛  疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we doing here, Crazy Legs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看咱们得来点实际行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought we could use some real action
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而最强人的事莫过于来点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what's tougher than a little
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,私闯民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,breaking and entering?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有自负的傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only a pretentious chump
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才住在那样一间又大又丑的人像屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would live in a big ugly head like that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这废物画的这么多丑画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check out the terrible paintings of this weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这废物看着好像你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This weenie looks like you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不像了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙快来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C'mon, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起修理这堆画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's fix these pics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:46.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262,252)}飞物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警察来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fuzz
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是公民逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a citizen's arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.37,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 公民逮捕：指非警察的公民\N逮捕犯罪嫌疑人的行为 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别逼我使出这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't make me use this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个血爆王的小废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the wimp from The Krusty Scab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来在给你家每晚例行安检呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just doing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my nightly security check of your house
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.80,0:20:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突然一清二楚地听见了打砸抢的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I heard the unmistakable sounds of vandalism
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.31,0:20:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫疯腿哥  这不是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The name's Crazy Legs, and this ain't my house
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够你跟你的童话故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had it with youse and your fairy tales
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,办了他  疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get him, Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准笑了  你个恼人的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing, you irritating stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么不记得我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定记得这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you remember this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.87,0:20:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只记得怎么使这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I remember is how to play this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他哪来的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd he get a bomb?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bomb?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're alive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我下去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这群恶棍都谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are all these ruffians?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会穿着这身俗气的皮衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why am I wearing all this tacky leather?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群流氓干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you delinquents do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们践踏了我的秋海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've trampled my begonias
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玷污了我的网眼小圆垫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And soiled my doilies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还毁坏了我无价的艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And vandalized my priceless art
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是疯腿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Crazy Legs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那都是你想出来的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that was all your idea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说原来这就是你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me this was your house all along?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course it is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯腿哥是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who is Crazy Legs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  大伙打包走人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, pack it up, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯腿哥原来是个无聊的老古董
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crazy Legs was just a boring old fuddy-duddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是后来失忆了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he got amnesia
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good riddance
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.16,0:21:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样洗劫民宅才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now dat's how ya ransack a house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯腿哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crazy Legs is back
